data.description: Colburn     This 3rd-Car Garage home offers 4 Bedrooms and 3 Bathrooms with a spacious guest suite and full bath on the main level. Private Wooded Lot. Spacious open loft area upstairs.  Formal Dining Room. The great room opens up to the kitchen. The kitchen has an island, a walk-in pantry, and a large mud room. Breakfast is separate from the kitchen. Upstairs has a Loft area, Primary Suite and Bathroom, 2 Secondary Bedrooms, Secondary Bathrooms, and a Laundry room. Primary's Bath has enlarged 7FT shower and walk in closet. SMART HOUSE PACKAGE Includes Ring Doorbell, Echo Show 8", Ecobee Thermostats & Kwikset Halo Smart Front Door Lock. Garage Door Opener (WIFI Enabled). Elegant Trim Package. ***PLEASE ASK THE ONSITE AGENT ABOUT OUR HUGE INCENTIVE!***CLOSE IN 30 DAYS!***
